criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-70 (this age range represents MOVE! eligibility);

          -  BMI of 30kg/m2 or a BMI of 25kg/m2 with obesity-associated condition;

          -  at least 1 prior PCP visit in the past 12 months; access to a telephone; ability to
             travel to Manhattan VA for in-person evaluations at baseline, 6 and 12 months;

          -  desire to lose weight (Using 1-10 scale used in PI's other studies; minimum of 4/10);

          -  willingness to enroll in the MOVE! program.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Non-Veterans;

          -  a documented current history of active psychosis or other cognitive issues via ICD-10
             codes;

          -  participating in a weight management study in the past year;

          -  taking an FDA-approved weight loss medication;

          -  pregnancy;

          -  PCP stating that Veteran should not participate.
